khoon ka rishta ( english : blood relation ) is a 1981 bollywood action film produced by &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; on &lt;unk&gt; productions banner and directed by samir ganguly . starring jeetendra , neetu singh in the lead roles and music composed by laxmikant-pyarelal . the film was a remake of telugu film khoon ka rishta ( 1981 ) .